ina Elias","date":"May 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe virtue of prayer in Masjid al-Haram is one hundred thousand times better than prayer elsewhere, prayer in this mosque of mine is one thousand times better than prayer elsewhere, and prayer in Bayt al-Maqdis is better than\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5635,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/29\/qiblah-al-quds-to-makkah\/","url_meta":{"origin":3042,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Qiblah: Changing direction of prayer from Jerusalem to Mecca","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, used to pray towards the Sacred House in Jerusalem, then it was revealed to him, \u201cWe have certainly seen you turning your face to the heaven. We will surely turn you to a direction of prayer\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13557,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/13\/tahiyyat-al-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":3042,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Greet mosque with Tahiyyatul Masjid prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen 